<b>MARINE</b>
<b>Those who assist criminals</b>

252
00:06:51.050 --> 00:06:51.090
<b>MARINE</b>

253
00:06:51.970 --> 00:06:53.100
[RIKA gasps]

254
00:06:53.100 --> 00:06:54.480
[HELMEPPO laughs]

255
00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:57.560
It seems even
little brats fear my daddy.

256
00:06:58.060 --> 00:06:59.570
His daddy?

257
00:06:59.570 --> 00:07:01.860
So that guy's father
is Captain Morgan?

258
00:07:02.280 --> 00:07:02.990
You!

259
00:07:02.990 --> 00:07:04.490
Toss this kid out right now.

260
00:07:04.490 --> 00:07:05.110
[MARINE gasps]

261
00:07:06.110 --> 00:07:08.700
I said, throw her over the wall, soldier!

262
00:07:08.700 --> 00:07:10.790
Now if you won't follow my orders,

263
00:07:10.790 --> 00:07:12.370
I'll tell my father.

264
00:07:12.370 --> 00:07:13.910
Yes, sir! I-I'll do it!

265
00:07:13.910 --> 00:07:14.660
[RIKA whimpering]

266
00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:16.790
No!

267
00:07:16.790 --> 00:07:21.380
[RIKA screaming]

268
00:07:17.790 --> 00:07:23.380
[energetic music]

269
00:07:24.760 --> 00:07:26.380
Thanks, mister!

270
00:07:26.380 --> 00:07:27.930
[KOBY]
Luffy! Are you two okay?!

271
00:07:28.840 --> 00:07:30.180
What about you, little girl?

272
00:07:30.180 --> 00:07:31.100
Are you all right?

273
00:07:31.100 --> 00:07:33.640
I can't believe how
wretched a person he is.

274
00:07:33.640 --> 00:07:34.850
Now where are you hurt? Anywhere?

275
00:07:35.290 --> 00:07:36.100
[ZORO]
Damn you.

276
00:07:36.100 --> 00:07:40.560
[HELMEPPO laughing]

277
00:07:40.940 --> 00:07:44.070
You're just dead set on
staying alive, aren't you?

278
00:07:44.070 --> 00:07:44.780
[ZORO]
That's right.

279
00:07:44.780 --> 00:07:47.070
And I'm gonna make it through
the month without any problems.

280
00:07:47.070 --> 00:07:48.950
[HELMEPPO]
Right... Good luck with that.

281
00:07:48.950 --> 00:07:51.950
[HELMEPPO cackling]

282
00:07:51.950 --> 00:07:54.040
Only ten days left!

283
00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:57.080
[HELMEPPO]
Oh, you still assume you'll make it
to the end of those ten days.

284
00:07:57.080 --> 00:07:58.420
[HELMEPPO cackles]

285
00:07:58.750 --> 00:08:01.420
[KOBY]
How can that man be so cruel?

286
00:08:01.420 --> 00:08:02.210
Luffy?

287
00:08:02.590 --> 00:08:04.420
Uh! What the...?
Where did he go?!

288
00:08:05.380 --> 00:08:06.130
[ZORO gasps]

289
00:08:06.670 --> 00:08:09.010
[LUFFY]
So, I hear you're a bad guy.

290
00:08:09.010 --> 00:08:10.430
[ZORO]
Are you still here?

291
00:08:10.430 --> 00:08:13.350
[LUFFY]
You're stuck out here for
all the world to see and nothing.

292
00:08:13.350 --> 00:08:14.680
Are you really all that strong?

293
00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:16.020
[ZORO]
Mind your own business!

294
00:08:16.020 --> 00:08:17.520
[LUFFY sighs]

295
00:08:18.640 --> 00:08:21.980
If I were you, I'd probably
starve to death in three days.

296
00:08:21.980 --> 00:08:24.480
[ZORO]
I've got more spirit
than you could ever have...

297
00:08:25.030 --> 00:08:28.240
which is how I'm gonna
survive this ordeal.

298
00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:29.990
This I swear.

299
00:08:29.990 --> 00:08:32.240
Hah, what a weirdo!

300
00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:33.490
[ZORO]
Wait, hold on.

301
00:08:34.540 --> 00:08:35.620
Could you...

302
00:08:35.620 --> 00:08:36.580
pick that up for me?

303
00:08:37.830 --> 00:08:40.000
You're gonna eat this?

304
00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:41.920
'Cause it's mostly a ball of mud.

305
00:08:41.920 --> 00:08:43.540
Shut up and give it to me, now!

306
00:08:48.220 --> 00:08:50.050
[ZORO coughing]

307
00:08:50.050 --> 00:08:51.720
Should've listened to me.

308
00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:53.180
[ZORO]
It was good.

309
00:08:54.060 --> 00:08:55.640
Thanks for the food.

310
00:08:57.770 --> 00:08:59.100
[RIKA]
Really?

311
00:08:59.850 --> 00:09:00.900
That's right!

312
00:09:00.900 --> 00:09:03.480
He ate every last
grain of rice there was.

313
00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:04.980
That's great!

314
00:09:04.980 --> 00:09:08.440
I wonder if Zoro was really as
evil as everyone thinks that he is.

315
00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:09.900
He's not!

316
00:09:10.450 --> 00:09:12.110
He's good... because...

317
00:09:12.450 --> 00:09:15.080
he got himself punished... for us.

318
00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:17.200
[LUFFY]
You're, uh... You're making no sense.

319
00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:18.040
[RIKA]
Sorry...

320
00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:19.710
It's that dumb Helmeppo.

321
00:09:19.710 --> 00:09:20.870
[sinister orchestral music]

322
00:09:20.870 --> 00:09:23.330
He's the son of Captain Morgan.

323
00:09:24.340 --> 00:09:26.500
[HELMEPPO]
Step aside! Step aside!

324
00:09:26.500 --> 00:09:28.670
Make way for my beautiful pet doggy!

325
00:09:29.050 --> 00:09:31.840
Anyone who doesn't move,
I'll have executed!

326
00:09:31.840 --> 00:09:33.640
[HELMEPPO laughs]

327
00:09:33.640 --> 00:09:35.430
– [WOLF snarls]
– [CROWD screams]

328
00:09:35.430 --> 00:09:35.970
[RIKA screams]

329
00:09:36.890 --> 00:09:38.520
[MAN screams]

330
00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:41.350
Stop it, you mean ol' thing!

331
00:09:41.350 --> 00:09:42.690
You, little girl!

332
00:09:42.690 --> 00:09:46.070
Is there some kind of problem with
how my beloved dog is behaving?

333
00:09:46.070 --> 00:09:47.610
Rika, put it down!

334
00:09:47.610 --> 00:09:49.240
You don't want to get us in trouble.

335
00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:52.530
[HELMEPPO snickering]

336
00:09:52.530 --> 00:09:53.450
[RIKA screaming]

337
00:09:54.240 --> 00:09:55.370
[HELMEPPO screams, gasps]

338
00:09:58.040 --> 00:10:00.040
[CROWD chatters]

339
00:10:02.210 --> 00:10:05.380
[RIKA]
Helmeppo keeps punching and
kicking him while he's tied up.

340
00:10:05.380 --> 00:10:06.670
He's being so unfair!

341
00:10:07.290 --> 00:10:08.670
I don't...

342
00:10:08.670 --> 00:10:10.090
I don't know how to help him!

343
00:10:10.090 --> 00:10:11.630
I see why you're upset.

344
00:10:10.760 --> 00:10:11.630
[RIKA cries]

345
00:10:11.630 --> 00:10:13.130
[glass shatters]

346
00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:15.470
I'm hungry.

347
00:10:15.470 --> 00:10:18.010
Bring us whatever you got
and keep the check for yourself.

348
00:10:18.010 --> 00:10:22.020
And bring me a bottle of your finest
moonshine or whatever crap you serve.

349
00:10:22.810 --> 00:10:24.730
I'm trying to think of
something interesting to do

350
00:10:24.730 --> 00:10:27.110
seeing as how I'm bored
out of my skull here.

351
00:10:27.110 --> 00:10:29.190
I suppose I can execute Zoro.

352
00:10:29.190 --> 00:10:32.740
[HELMEPPO cackling]

353
00:10:32.740 --> 00:10:36.570
[energetic music]

354
00:10:38.580 --> 00:10:40.200
You... You just hit me!

355
00:10:40.200 --> 00:10:41.120
[KOBY] Luffy, no!

356
00:10:40.620 --> 00:10:44.120
[HELMEPPO whimpering]

357
00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:42.370
You can't hit him!

358
00:10:42.370 --> 00:10:44.120
[LUFFY] This guy is scum!

359
00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:46.000
You actually hit me!

360
00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:48.630
I am Captain Morgan's son, you know!

361
00:10:48.630 --> 00:10:49.800
[LUFFY]
Yeah, like I care!

362
00:10:50.130 --> 00:10:52.760
You'll care after
he executes you for this!

363
00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:54.930
Why don't you just
be a man and fight?!

364
00:10:54.930 --> 00:10:56.510
Luffy, just ease off some!

365
00:10:56.510 --> 00:10:58.850
Why are you trying to get
on the Marines' bad side?!

366
00:10:58.850 --> 00:10:59.850
[LUFFY]
I've made up my mind.

367
00:10:59.850 --> 00:11:00.510
[KOBY gasps]

368
00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:02.890
Today...

369
00:11:03.480 --> 00:11:05.520
Zoro joins my crew.

370
00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:11.360
[MORGAN]
I am...

371
00:11:11.360 --> 00:11:12.570
great!

372
00:11:12.570 --> 00:11:13.490
[MARINE]
Yes, sir!

373
00:11:13.490 --> 00:11:15.490
You are right, Captain Morgan, sir!

374
00:11:15.490 --> 00:11:20.030
[MORGAN]
And yet, the taxes we collect don't even
compare to my sheer degree of greatness.

375
00:11:20.030 --> 00:11:21.410
Yes, right, sir.

376
00:11:21.410 --> 00:11:24.750
I guess that the citizens' wallets
just aren't very deep these days, sir.

377
00:11:24.750 --> 00:11:28.670
[MORGAN]
The issue at hand here
is their level of respect for me.

378
00:11:29.210 --> 00:11:30.460
Wouldn't you agree?

379
00:11:30.460 --> 00:11:31.420
[HELMEPPO sobbing]

380
00:11:32.340 --> 00:11:33.170
Daddy!

381
00:11:33.170 --> 00:11:33.670
[MORGAN]
Hm?

382
00:11:33.670 --> 00:11:36.220
There's someone outside
that I want you to slaughter,

383
00:11:36.220 --> 00:11:37.970
and I want it done now!

384
00:11:39.300 --> 00:11:40.720
[ZORO sighs]

385
00:11:41.680 --> 00:11:42.180
Huh?

386
00:11:43.140 --> 00:11:44.480
[scoffs] You again...

387
00:11:44.480 --> 00:11:45.850
Don't you have things to do?

388
00:11:45.850 --> 00:11:48.690
[LUFFY]
I'll untie you, but only if
you promise to join my crew.

389
00:11:48.690 --> 00:11:49.810
[ZORO]
Your what?

390
00:11:49.810 --> 00:11:52.650
[LUFFY]
I run a pirate crew, and I'm
looking for people to join up.

391
00:11:53.320 --> 00:11:54.440
No way!

392
00:11:54.440 --> 00:11:57.030
I'd never stoop to
joining up with a criminal.

393
00:11:57.030 --> 00:11:58.320
Screw that business.

394
00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:00.700
And what's wrong with being a pirate?

395
00:12:00.700 --> 00:12:01.580
[ZORO]
They're despicable!

396
00:12:01.580 --> 00:12:03.120
Like I'd ever wanna join up with one.

397
00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:04.290
Oh, come on! Gimme a break.

398
00:12:04.660 --> 00:12:08.250
Everyone already knows you as some
vicious bounty hunter always out for blood.

399
00:12:08.250 --> 00:12:10.960
People can say whatever
they want about me,

400
00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:13.710
but I've never done a single
thing in my life that I regret.

401
00:12:14.510 --> 00:12:16.920
I will make it through this challenge.

402
00:12:16.920 --> 00:12:19.680
And after that,
I'll accomplish what I want.

403
00:12:19.970 --> 00:12:21.850
Yeah... That's great.

404
00:12:22.220 --> 00:12:24.810
But I've already decided that
you're going to be on my crew.

405
00:12:24.810 --> 00:12:26.310
What?! You can't do that!

406
00:12:26.310 --> 00:12:28.100
I hear you're one of
the best swordsmen around.

407
00:12:28.100 --> 00:12:29.400
[ZORO]
Well, I am!

408
00:12:29.400 --> 00:12:32.230
But that idiot Captain's son
took mine away.

409
00:12:32.230 --> 00:12:33.820
Guess I'll just have to
go get it back for you.

410
00:12:33.820 --> 00:12:34.320
[ZORO] What?

411
00:12:34.690 --> 00:12:37.900
So if you want your sword,
you're just gonna have to join my crew!

412
00:12:37.900 --> 00:12:39.280
Now you're really pissing me off!

413
00:12:39.280 --> 00:12:41.200
[LUFFY laughs]

414
00:12:41.200 --> 00:12:44.120
Wait, he's actually
gonna bust in there alone?

415
00:12:44.450 --> 00:12:49.540
[MARINES]
Heave ho! Heave ho!

416
00:12:49.830 --> 00:12:53.290
Heave ho! Heave ho!

417
00:12:53.290 --> 00:12:55.460
[MORGAN]
That's it! Stop right there.

418
00:12:55.460 --> 00:12:58.220
Now stand it up in one final pull!

419
00:12:58.970 --> 00:12:59.720
Well, dad?

420
00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:02.140
Are you gonna get revenge
on this guy or what?!

421
00:13:02.140 --> 00:13:04.810
I mean he just outright
struck me in public!

422
00:13:04.810 --> 00:13:07.770
You've never hit me before!
Why should he be able to?

423
00:13:07.770 --> 00:13:12.150
[MORGAN]
Do you have any remote idea
as to why I've never hit you?

424
00:13:12.520 --> 00:13:13.360
Well?

425
00:13:13.360 --> 00:13:16.150
Uh... Is it because
you think I'm great?

426
00:13:16.820 --> 00:13:18.360
[MORGAN]
No...

427
00:13:18.360 --> 00:13:20.240
...it's because...

428
00:13:21.160 --> 00:13:22.490
[HELMEPPO screams]

429
00:13:23.660 --> 00:13:26.740
[menacing orchestral music]

430
00:13:26.240 --> 00:13:31.620
<b>"Axe-Hand" Morgan
Marine Captain</b>

431
00:13:26.740 --> 00:13:29.410
[MORGAN] ...you're a stupid fool...

432
00:13:29.410 --> 00:13:31.620
who isn't even worth hitting.

433
00:13:31.620 --> 00:13:34.500
I don't want you to get the wrong idea.

434
00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:34.500
[HELMEPPO yelping]

435
00:13:37.760 --> 00:13:39.840
The only great one around here

436
00:13:39.840 --> 00:13:41.680
is the man you call your father!

437
00:13:42.840 --> 00:13:44.430
[HELMEPPO groans]

438
00:13:44.430 --> 00:13:45.720
[MORGAN]
Which reminds me.

439
00:13:45.720 --> 00:13:48.680
I heard a rat snuck into
the crucifixion yard.

440
00:13:48.680 --> 00:13:49.850
[HELMEPPO gasps]

441
00:13:49.850 --> 00:13:53.270
Yes. That's right, the little girl,
b-but I-I had her dealt with.

442
00:13:53.270 --> 00:13:54.650
I hope that means killed.

443
00:13:54.650 --> 00:13:58.110
No, I... I didn't kill her.
She's just a kid...

444
00:13:58.940 --> 00:13:59.860
[MORGAN]
You there!

445
00:13:59.860 --> 00:14:02.280
Go into town,
find this girl, and kill her!

446
00:14:02.280 --> 00:14:05.570
But... sir! You can't be serious...

447
00:14:05.570 --> 00:14:07.080
She's just a little girl, sir.

448
00:14:07.080 --> 00:14:09.200
[MORGAN]
I don't care if she's a child or not!

449
00:14:09.200 --> 00:14:12.080
Anyone who disobeys
my orders is a traitor!

450
00:14:12.080 --> 00:14:12.960
[LIEUTENANT]
No, sir...

451
00:14:13.710 --> 00:14:14.920
I can't do it.

452
00:14:18.500 --> 00:14:19.800
[HELMEPPO screams]

453
00:14:19.800 --> 00:14:20.840
[MARINES]
Lieutenant!

454
00:14:21.550 --> 00:14:23.180
You... You killed him!

455
00:14:23.930 --> 00:14:28.060
My strength was what I used
to rise to the rank of captain.

456
00:14:28.600 --> 00:14:29.770
Listen!

457
00:14:29.770 --> 00:14:32.020
In this world,
titles are what matter!

458
00:14:32.390 --> 00:14:36.650
That means by being the captain of
this base and the highest ranking officer,

459
00:14:36.650 --> 00:14:40.730
I am the most superior person
as far as the eye can see!

460
00:14:41.400 --> 00:14:42.860
This means...

461
00:14:42.860 --> 00:14:45.320
that I do everything right!

462
00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:47.570
Am I correct, men?!

463
00:14:47.910 --> 00:14:49.700
Sir! You are correct, sir!

464
00:14:49.700 --> 00:14:52.660
[MORGAN]
Let's put killing the girl
on hold for now.

465
00:14:52.660 --> 00:14:56.500
Observe, the greatest symbol
of my unending authority.

466
00:14:56.920 --> 00:15:00.170
It took years to complete,
but here it is.

467
00:15:00.170 --> 00:15:01.710
Now stand it up!

468
00:15:00.170 --> 00:15:01.880
[MARINES] Heave ho!

469
00:15:01.880 --> 00:15:09.720
Heave ho! Heave ho!
Heave ho! Heave ho! Heave ho!

470
00:15:02.380 --> 00:15:06.180
[MORGAN]
Display my greatness at
the top of this base for all to see!

471
00:15:09.720 --> 00:15:10.760
[LUFFY]
That's weird...

472
00:15:10.760 --> 00:15:11.810
There's nobody here.

473
00:15:12.060 --> 00:15:15.770
I gotta find that crazy idiot son
and get Zoro's sword back for him.

474
00:15:15.770 --> 00:15:16.440
Huh?

475
00:15:16.440 --> 00:15:19.400
[MARINES]
Heave ho! Heave ho!

476
00:15:16.940 --> 00:15:18.230
[MORGAN]
Pull, men!

477
00:15:18.230 --> 00:15:19.400
Harder!

478
00:15:19.400 --> 00:15:23.570
Heave ho! Heave ho! Heave ho!

479
00:15:23.570 --> 00:15:24.320
[MARINE yelps]

480
00:15:24.320 --> 00:15:26.030
[MORGAN]
You there!

481
00:15:26.030 --> 00:15:27.570
[MARINE yelps, whimpers]

482
00:15:29.070 --> 00:15:30.330
[MORGAN]
You bumped it.

483
00:15:30.330 --> 00:15:31.290
[LUFFY]
Hm?

484
00:15:31.620 --> 00:15:34.000
Sounds like something's
goin' on up there.

485
00:15:35.080 --> 00:15:36.330
I'm sorry, sir!

486
00:15:36.330 --> 00:15:38.040
I was reckless! I didn't mean it!

487
00:15:38.040 --> 00:15:40.540
[MORGAN]
I consider the
slightest scratch on this...

488
00:15:40.920 --> 00:15:42.340
nothing less...

489
00:15:42.340 --> 00:15:46.510
than a traitorous activity
that's punishable by death!

490
00:15:46.510 --> 00:15:49.010
[energetic string music]

491
00:15:46.510 --> 00:15:48.260
Guess I should check it out.

492
00:15:49.010 --> 00:15:51.350
Gum Gum...

493
00:15:51.760 --> 00:15:52.760
Rocket!

494
00:15:52.760 --> 00:15:53.770
– [MORGAN yells]
– [MARINE whimpers]

495
00:15:54.180 --> 00:15:55.390
[LUFFY]
Huh-hoo!

496
00:15:55.390 --> 00:15:56.850
Wah... I jumped too far!

497
00:15:56.850 --> 00:15:57.640
[MORGAN]
Huh?

498
00:15:57.640 --> 00:15:58.900
What is that thing?!

499
00:15:58.900 --> 00:16:00.110
It flew up from the ground!

500
00:16:00.860 --> 00:16:02.900
– [LUFFY] Got it!
– [MARINES gasping]

501
00:16:02.900 --> 00:16:04.570
[MARINES screaming]

502
00:16:04.570 --> 00:16:07.530
[MARINES grunting]

503
00:16:07.530 --> 00:16:08.530
[MORGAN gasps]

504
00:16:08.530 --> 00:16:11.240
[HELMEPPO, MARINES scream]

505
00:16:13.830 --> 00:16:15.000
[LUFFY]
Sorry about that.

506
00:16:17.710 --> 00:16:20.670
[menacing orchestral music]
Seize him and hold him,
so I can kill him myself!

507
00:16:20.670 --> 00:16:22.130
[MARINES]
Sir! Right away!

508
00:16:22.130 --> 00:16:23.340
That's him! That's the guy!

509
00:16:23.340 --> 00:16:25.670
He's the one who punched me, daddy!

510
00:16:24.630 --> 00:16:25.670
[LUFFY] Hey, it's you!

511
00:16:26.170 --> 00:16:27.170
[screaming]

512
00:16:27.170 --> 00:16:29.050
I've been looking for you
all over the place.

513
00:16:29.050 --> 00:16:30.970
You have something
that I really need to get back.

514
00:16:31.550 --> 00:16:32.470
[HELMEPPO] Let me go!

515
00:16:31.970 --> 00:16:33.390
[MARINES] Helmeppo!

516
00:16:32.470 --> 00:16:33.390
[HELMEPPO] Someone help me!

517
00:16:33.390 --> 00:16:35.600
[MORGAN]
Do not let that man escape!

518
00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:36.230
[MARINE]
Captain!

519
00:16:36.230 --> 00:16:38.140
There's someone in
the crucifixion yard!

520
00:16:38.140 --> 00:16:39.190
What?!

521
00:16:43.820 --> 00:16:45.820
I'm surrounded...

522
00:16:45.820 --> 00:16:47.650
by traitors.

523
00:16:47.650 --> 00:16:49.610
[KOBY]
You have to get out of here, Zoro.

524
00:16:49.610 --> 00:16:52.490
That maniac's going to kill you
for what you're doin' right now!

525
00:16:52.490 --> 00:16:56.160
[KOBY]
I can't stand to watch the Marines
behave like this anymore.

526
00:16:56.830 --> 00:16:59.040
A true Marine should be honorable.

527
00:16:59.410 --> 00:17:01.210
Look, kid, I can't leave!

528
00:17:01.210 --> 00:17:03.250
I got ten days left.
And, then they're–

529
00:17:03.250 --> 00:17:05.460
Well, not quite. They're gonna
execute you tomorrow.

530
00:17:05.460 --> 00:17:06.340
They're what?

531
00:17:06.340 --> 00:17:11.430
[apprehensive string music]

532
00:17:06.340 --> 00:17:09.090
[KOBY]
Helmeppo never intended
to honor your agreement.

533
00:17:09.090 --> 00:17:11.430
He planned on
killing you from the start.

534
00:17:11.430 --> 00:17:15.010
Which made Luffy really angry,
so he just knocked him out.

535
00:17:16.140 --> 00:17:17.100
He did?

536
00:17:17.100 --> 00:17:21.020
Now that the Marines are mad,
they're dead set on catching Luffy.

537
00:17:21.020 --> 00:17:24.230
Don't worry, I'm not gonna ask
you to become a pirate, though.

538
00:17:24.230 --> 00:17:25.610
But I hope you'll help him.

539
00:17:25.940 --> 00:17:28.110
You have a lot of
strength you can offer.

540
00:17:31.570 --> 00:17:35.990
Luffy's the only person here who can
actually save you from execution.

541
00:17:37.040 --> 00:17:38.500
And of course...

542
00:17:38.500 --> 00:17:43.540
you're the only one here who can
save him from a very similar fate.

543
00:17:45.090 --> 00:17:46.670
[MORGAN]
End of the line!

544
00:17:48.340 --> 00:17:50.050
[energetic music]
[HELPMEPPO screaming]

545
00:17:50.050 --> 00:17:51.880
Okay, so tell me where
Zoro's sword is.

546
00:17:51.880 --> 00:17:53.640
[HELMEPPO]
I'll tell you! I promise!

547
00:17:53.640 --> 00:17:56.470
Just please stop dragging
me across the carpet...

548
00:17:56.470 --> 00:17:57.350
Fine, which way?

549
00:17:57.350 --> 00:17:57.970
In my room.

550
00:17:57.970 --> 00:18:00.600
We just passed it,
behind you on the left.

551
00:18:00.600 --> 00:18:02.600
Why didn't you say so earlier?

552
00:18:02.600 --> 00:18:04.060
Now we gotta go all the way back.

553
00:18:04.060 --> 00:18:05.230
[MARINE A]
Don't move!

554
00:18:05.230 --> 00:18:06.820
[MARINE B]
Except for letting Helmeppo go!

555
00:18:07.190 --> 00:18:08.400
No way.

556
00:18:09.900 --> 00:18:12.070
But you can try
shooting me if you want.

557
00:18:12.070 --> 00:18:14.160
[HELMEPPO]
No! Please don't shoot!

558
00:18:14.160 --> 00:18:15.950
Don't! Get the hell outta the way!

559
00:18:15.950 --> 00:18:18.870
[MORGAN]
For the crime of treason against me,

560
00:18:18.870 --> 00:18:22.000
I sentence you both
to die where you stand.

561
00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:23.250
[KOBY yelps]

562
00:18:24.920 --> 00:18:26.000
This looks like yours.

563
00:18:29.840 --> 00:18:30.960
[LUFFY]
Bingo!

564
00:18:31.970 --> 00:18:33.840
Hold on. There are three here.

565
00:18:33.840 --> 00:18:35.930
Hey, weirdo, which one
of these is Zoro's?

566
00:18:35.930 --> 00:18:36.800
[HELMEPPO whimpering]

567
00:18:36.800 --> 00:18:38.680
[LUFFY]
Guess he passed out.

568
00:18:39.680 --> 00:18:40.390
[gasps]

569
00:18:40.390 --> 00:18:41.680
Koby!

570
00:18:41.680 --> 00:18:44.650
[menacing orchestral music]
[KOBY whimpering]

571
00:18:48.610 --> 00:18:51.690
You've been pulling some
interesting moves around here.

572
00:18:51.690 --> 00:18:52.570
What is this?

573
00:18:52.570 --> 00:18:58.120
Some kind of poorly executed coup
you two planned with the straw hat?

574
00:18:58.120 --> 00:19:00.580
[ZORO]
I've always fought alone
like a real man does.

575
00:19:00.580 --> 00:19:02.040
Not like a coward...

576
00:19:02.040 --> 00:19:05.040
who hides behind his
wall of expendable cronies.

577
00:19:05.040 --> 00:19:07.080
[MORGAN]
Roronoa Zoro.

578
00:19:07.080 --> 00:19:09.500
Don't you dare underestimate me.

579
00:19:09.920 --> 00:19:13.090
You may be a strong fighter,
but under my authority,

580
00:19:13.090 --> 00:19:15.930
you're just the rat we
throw out with the trash.

581
00:19:15.930 --> 00:19:17.010
Take aim!

582
00:19:17.010 --> 00:19:18.140
[ZORO]
No...

583
00:19:21.180 --> 00:19:23.600
[ZORO]
I can't afford to die here!

584
00:19:27.730 --> 00:19:30.730
[INSTRUCTOR]
Match over! And the winner...

585
00:19:30.730 --> 00:19:34.240
Kuina! With 2,000 total
wins and zero losses.

586
00:19:34.240 --> 00:19:36.910
[ZORO groaning]
Damn it.

587
00:19:36.910 --> 00:19:40.240
[KUINA]
You're weak, Zoro.
Nothing ever changes.

588
00:19:40.580 --> 00:19:43.700
You know, for a boy, you're pathetic.

589
00:19:43.700 --> 00:19:45.750
But, Zoro isn't weak at all.

590
00:19:45.750 --> 00:19:48.040
He's one of the strongest
out of all the guys.

591
00:19:48.040 --> 00:19:49.630
[STUDENT C]
He's even beaten grownups.

592
00:19:49.630 --> 00:19:50.670
–[KUINA] But...
–[STUDENTS whimper]

593
00:19:50.670 --> 00:19:52.750
[KUINA]
He's nowhere as strong as me.

594
00:19:52.750 --> 00:19:56.010
Even with two swords,
a weakling is still a weakling.

595
00:19:56.010 --> 00:19:58.930
You losers would do good to
remember that and keep quiet.

596
00:19:58.930 --> 00:20:02.180
Your howling makes you look even
more pitiful than you already are.

597
00:20:11.060 --> 00:20:13.400
[KOSHIRO]
You've grown so strong, Zoro.

598
00:20:13.400 --> 00:20:17.070
And yet, you continue to lose
every match against Kuina.

599
00:20:17.070 --> 00:20:17.990
[STUDENT]
Sensei!

600
00:20:17.990 --> 00:20:20.200
Are you giving her special training?!

601
00:20:20.200 --> 00:20:22.490
She might be your daughter,
but that's not fair!

602
00:20:22.490 --> 00:20:23.540
You shouldn't cheat!

603
00:20:23.910 --> 00:20:26.620
Calm down. I've done
nothing of the sort.

604
00:20:27.410 --> 00:20:30.210
You see, Zoro has grown stronger.

605
00:20:30.210 --> 00:20:33.880
But, Kuina has continued
to grow stronger as well.

606
00:20:34.630 --> 00:20:35.210
[STUDENT A]
Zoro!

607
00:20:35.210 --> 00:20:36.550
[STUDENT B]
Zoro...?

608
00:20:36.550 --> 00:20:38.590
[ZORO]
I'm gonna go clean up.

609
00:20:38.590 --> 00:20:41.930
[water splashing]

610
00:20:44.680 --> 00:20:45.430
[ZORO growls]

611
00:20:45.890 --> 00:20:48.560
[ZORO]
Damn it! Why can't I beat Kuina?!

612
00:20:48.560 --> 00:20:49.770
Why?! Why?!

613
00:20:49.770 --> 00:20:52.860
I'm going to be the
strongest swordsman in the world!

614
00:20:52.860 --> 00:20:54.820
So why can't I beat her?!

615
00:20:54.820 --> 00:20:56.280
[apprehensive music]

616
00:21:05.240 --> 00:21:06.370
[KUINA]
Zoro?

617
00:21:06.370 --> 00:21:08.620
It's late out. What are you doing?

618
00:21:09.120 --> 00:21:12.170
Funny. I was gonna ask
you the same question.

619
00:21:12.170 --> 00:21:14.040
What are you doing out so late?

620
00:21:16.090 --> 00:21:19.840
I've come here to challenge you
to your 2,001st fight.

621
00:21:19.840 --> 00:21:23.430
And it's gonna be the last fight
you and me will ever have.

622
00:21:23.430 --> 00:21:25.100
This ends tonight.

623
00:21:25.100 --> 00:21:27.390
Fight me with a real sword!

624
00:21:27.390 --> 00:21:29.180
You do have one, don't you?

625
00:21:31.810 --> 00:21:32.940
Real swords...?

626
00:21:36.980 --> 00:21:38.070
You're on.

627
00:21:48.950 --> 00:21:51.290
[energetic orchestral music]

628
00:21:54.710 --> 00:21:55.170
[ZORO grunts]

629
00:21:56.090 --> 00:21:56.590
[KUINA grunts]

630
00:22:00.590 --> 00:22:02.130
[ZORO growls]

631
00:22:03.760 --> 00:22:06.510
[ZORO screaming]

632
00:22:07.470 --> 00:22:07.970
[KUINA]
Ah!

633
00:22:14.940 --> 00:22:17.020
Win number 2,001.

634
00:22:21.530 --> 00:22:24.200
[ZORO crying]

635
00:22:24.200 --> 00:22:25.410
Damn it!

636
00:22:27.160 --> 00:22:29.120
I hate it!

637
00:22:29.120 --> 00:22:32.410
[mournful string music]
[ZORO crying]

638
00:22:32.750 --> 00:22:35.630
[KUINA]
I'm the one who should be
crying out of frustration.

639
00:22:35.630 --> 00:22:37.130
Not you.

640
00:22:39.550 --> 00:22:42.920
When girls grow up,
its natural for us to develop

641
00:22:42.920 --> 00:22:45.140
into physically weaker
beings than men.

642
00:22:46.340 --> 00:22:48.930
Even you will catch up
to me soon enough.

643
00:22:50.270 --> 00:22:52.600
I've always heard you say to me,

644
00:22:52.600 --> 00:22:55.020
you're gonna be the world's
greatest swordsman.

645
00:22:55.650 --> 00:22:57.940
When I told my father the same thing,

646
00:22:58.650 --> 00:23:00.860
he said I could never be that.

647
00:23:01.820 --> 00:23:05.030
And I know. I know that. But...

648
00:23:05.030 --> 00:23:07.030
It's just so frustrating.

649
00:23:09.240 --> 00:23:12.160
You're lucky Zoro,
being born as a man.

650
00:23:12.750 --> 00:23:15.790
All I ever wanted was to be
the world's greatest swordsman.

651
00:23:17.000 --> 00:23:19.500
My breasts have even
started to grow out now.

652
00:23:19.920 --> 00:23:21.210
If only...

653
00:23:21.210 --> 00:23:23.670
If I had just been born a man!

654
00:23:23.670 --> 00:23:24.970
[ZORO growls]

655
00:23:24.970 --> 00:23:28.930
[ZORO]
Don't fly off at the mouth,
whining like that after you beat me!

656
00:23:28.930 --> 00:23:31.100
Because it's not fair!
You're my goal!

657
00:23:31.100 --> 00:23:32.430
You know how this
makes me feel?!

658
00:23:32.930 --> 00:23:33.770
Zoro...

659
00:23:33.770 --> 00:23:35.020
[ZORO]
Boy this! Girl that!

660
00:23:35.020 --> 00:23:38.730
Are you gonna keep up that same
kinda talk after I beat you some day?!

661
00:23:38.730 --> 00:23:40.730
Like skill is irrelevant!

662
00:23:40.730 --> 00:23:44.400
That's just an insult to all of the training
I've been pouring on every day!

663
00:23:45.070 --> 00:23:47.320
So don't say that crap, would ya?!

664
00:23:49.410 --> 00:23:51.280
Now promise me...!

665
00:23:51.280 --> 00:23:55.790
Promise me that someday one of us
will be the world's greatest swordsman!

666
00:23:55.790 --> 00:23:57.500
We'll compete and see
who gets there.

667
00:24:02.090 --> 00:24:03.840
Dummy. You're so weak.

668
00:24:07.930 --> 00:24:09.510
[KUINA, ZORO]
It's a promise.

669
00:24:13.010 --> 00:24:17.230
[ZORO]
Gotta get stronger so
I can hold lots of swords.

670
00:24:17.230 --> 00:24:20.060
If two's not enough, I'll use three!

671
00:24:24.480 --> 00:24:26.400
[ZORO]
What do you guys want?

672
00:24:28.200 --> 00:24:29.320
Huh?

673
00:24:29.320 --> 00:24:30.660
[STUDENT]
Kuina...

674
00:24:31.700 --> 00:24:34.620
Kuina is dead, Zoro.

675
00:24:40.130 --> 00:24:43.090
[sorrowful music]

676
00:24:46.590 --> 00:24:49.510
[MAN A]
They said she slipped
and fell down the storehouse steps.

677
00:24:49.510 --> 00:24:51.050
[MAN B]
Storehouse?

678
00:24:51.050 --> 00:24:54.220
[MAN A]
Looking for a sharpening stone
for her beloved sword.

679
00:24:54.220 --> 00:24:56.100
[MAN B]
What would she need that for?

680
00:24:56.100 --> 00:24:57.310
[MAN A]
I don't know.

681
00:24:57.310 --> 00:24:59.270
[MAN B]
She was just a child, too.

682
00:24:59.270 --> 00:25:01.310
[MAN A]
Who knows why
anyone does anything.

683
00:25:01.650 --> 00:25:04.110
There's no way to rationalize it.

684
00:25:04.110 --> 00:25:07.190
[MAN B]
Guess you never know what's waiting
for you around the next corner.

685
00:25:14.120 --> 00:25:16.790
[KOSHIRO]
It may appear otherwise
to the blind eye,

686
00:25:16.790 --> 00:25:19.710
but people are quite fragile things.

687
00:25:20.500 --> 00:25:24.420
[soft music]
[ZORO sobbing]

688
00:25:33.510 --> 00:25:34.890
[ZORO]
Sensei...

689
00:25:36.430 --> 00:25:38.850
I ask that you let me have that sword.

690
00:25:41.350 --> 00:25:42.980
[KOSHIRO]
Kuina's sword?

691
00:25:44.310 --> 00:25:45.610
I'll get stronger!

692
00:25:45.610 --> 00:25:48.070
Stronger than she
ever was, you hear me?!

693
00:25:48.490 --> 00:25:51.860
Strong enough that my name
reaches up to the heavens!

694
00:25:52.860 --> 00:25:55.830
I am going to be
the world's greatest swordsman!

695
00:25:57.870 --> 00:25:59.790
I promised her.

696
00:25:59.790 --> 00:26:01.830
I promised...

697
00:26:02.250 --> 00:26:03.750
I did...

698
00:26:03.750 --> 00:26:06.800
[ZORO sobbing]

699
00:26:10.340 --> 00:26:12.220
[KOSHIRO]
The sword is yours.

700
00:26:12.220 --> 00:26:12.880
[ZORO gasps]

701
00:26:16.760 --> 00:26:19.890
I leave her spirit and her dreams...

702
00:26:19.890 --> 00:26:21.810
in your hands.

703
00:26:22.690 --> 00:26:24.810
[ZORO whimpering]

704
00:26:25.400 --> 00:26:32.740
[ZORO wailing]

705
00:26:46.460 --> 00:26:48.750
Gum Gum...

706
00:26:48.750 --> 00:26:49.920
Rocket!

707
00:26:49.920 --> 00:26:50.510
Fire!

708
00:26:54.880 --> 00:26:55.470
What?!

709
00:26:55.470 --> 00:26:56.510
Luffy, no!

710
00:26:56.510 --> 00:26:57.140
[MORGAN]
Straw Hat!

711
00:26:58.510 --> 00:27:00.470
[MARINES gasping]

712
00:27:01.020 --> 00:27:02.060
[LUFFY]
Heh.

713
00:27:02.930 --> 00:27:04.890
See ya!

714
00:27:06.150 --> 00:27:09.400
[LUFFY laughing]

715
00:27:08.190 --> 00:27:11.900
[monumental orchestral music]

716
00:27:09.400 --> 00:27:10.980
That won't work on me!

717
00:27:10.980 --> 00:27:12.440
Told ya I was strong!

718
00:27:12.440 --> 00:27:13.780
What the...?!

719
00:27:13.780 --> 00:27:15.070
Who the hell are you?

720
00:27:16.110 --> 00:27:18.580
My name's Monkey D. Luffy.

721
00:27:18.580 --> 00:27:21.370
And I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!

722
00:27:30.140 --> 00:27:37.000
As a kid, I had a dream of a dazzling treasure

723
00:27:37.200 --> 00:27:44.020
I had a map in my head that I knew would lead me

724
00:27:44.270 --> 00:27:51.120
Charted a course all on my own, so nobody would beat me

725
00:27:51.240 --> 00:27:58.380
The promised land was in my hand, drew a line in the sand

726
00:28:01.080 --> 00:28:03.760
Look where I am

727
00:28:05.990 --> 00:28:12.170
My one ambition's slipping right through my hands

728
00:28:12.510 --> 00:28:19.440
But if the world ever changes I'll call out your name

729
00:28:19.600 --> 00:28:26.520
We could return to a time when our lives were still the same

730
00:28:26.650 --> 00:28:33.650
Take me to the place where memories remain

731
00:28:33.750 --> 00:28:39.520
Please don't ever let them fade
